DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,9,1);
$b = random(2,5,1);
$d = random(1,5,1);
$c = $d - 4;

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Evaluate the integral by interpreting it in terms of areas:
$BR
$PAR
\( \displaystyle{ \int_{$c}^{$d} ($a - $b x)\, dx} = \)
$PAR
   \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
$BR

EOT

$ans = $a*$d - .5*$b*($d)**2 - $a*$c + .5*$b*($c)**2;

ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();
